        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/d9b06d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-12-28T03:00:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Howdy Jeremy, and Merry Christmas!  If my memory is correct, '76 was an unusual vintage in Burgundy - tannic and misbehaving when youthful.  And Faiveley made rather sturdy wines to begin with! I haven\u2019t had any '76s in quite a while, but I\u2019m not entirely surprised that one is finally showing well! :=)</p>",
