        "created_at": "2017-12-28T15:37:18.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Thanks for the reminder Jeremy - I have some red 76 in the cellar that I should try to unearth! I finished my whites at the beginning of the year - and for the last 10 years they were magnificent.<br>\n76 not a hot vintage like in the UK that year, but it was as dry as any on record - virtually nil rain between March and October!</p>",
